title: Dutch Hill (Delaware County, New York)
text: Dutch Hill is a <a href="mountain">mountain</a> located in the <a href="Catskill%20Mountains">Catskill Mountains</a> of <a href="New%20York%20%28state%29">New York</a> east of <a href="Davenport%20Center%2C%20New%20York">Davenport Center</a>. <a href="Webb%20Hill%20%28New%20York%29">Webb Hill</a> is located northwest, and <a href="Mine%20Hill%20%28New%20York%29">Mine Hill</a> is located southwest of Dutch Hill.
